	(Output_data_plt_x86_64::do_add_eh_frame): New abstract virtual method.
	(Output_data_plt_x86_64::add_eh_frame): New method to call it.
	(Output_data_plt_x86_64::do_fill_first_plt_entry): New abstract
	virtual method.
