	(Output_data_plt_x86_64::do_fill_tlsdesc_entry): New abstract
	virtual method.
	(Output_data_plt_x86_64::fill_tlsdesc_entry): New method to call it.
	(Output_data_plt_x86_64::plt_entry_size)
